00:16:12.972 --> 00:16:15.573
tjerati malu djevojčicu
da se bori za to

00:16:15.575 --> 00:16:18.309
za vrednovanje stranaca.

00:16:23.349 --> 00:16:26.317
To je sve o čemu je
moja majka brinula.

00:16:28.053 --> 00:16:29.687
Žao mi je, dušo.

00:16:30.823 --> 00:16:34.225
To je to.
