00:17:14.567 --> 00:17:16.401
Vidjeću šta mogu uraditi, Susan.

00:17:16.403 --> 00:17:20.271
Znate, mislim da možete
uraditi više nego vidjeti.

00:17:20.273 --> 00:17:23.775
Ne mogu to prihvatiti.
- Naravno da možete.

00:17:23.777 --> 00:17:27.111
To je njen život,
to je sve što ima.

00:17:30.316 --> 00:17:32.115
Dobro.

00:17:32.351 --> 00:17:35.219
Čaj?
